  <brief_title>Quality of Life of Patients With Psoriasis Treated With Methotrexate: Prospective, Randomized, Double-blind, Parallel Group Study.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Improvement in the Quality of Life of Patients With Severe Plaque Psoriasis Treated With Systemic Methotrexate in Fixed Doses of 10mg or 25mg Orally Once Weekly: a Prospective, Randomized, Double-blind, Parallel Group Study.</official_title>
