  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Methotrexate (MTX) is considered the 'gold-standard' drug for the treatment of severe
      psoriasis. Health-related quality of life (HRQOL) is impaired in patients with psoriasis,
      more so if disease is severe.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
