  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        Age range 18 to 65 years Both sexes Severe plaque-type psoriasis (BSA &gt;10% or PASI &gt;12) -

        Exclusion Criteria:

        Pregnancy Lactation Malignancy or immunosuppression including HIV Liver disease Renal
        disease Non compliant Psychiatric illness Hypersensitivity to methotrexate in the past
      </textblock>
